WORK BEGINS AT HOME
  Billy has received the requirments from his client, given thought to the layout, and gotten approval from the client.  He is all ready to go.  Billy was told that this site should feel sleek, mature, and fluid.  It's time for Billy to start writing code and it all starts with the Home Page.
  
